reviewText:
A totally enjoyable series. Played a part of it last night on our new "Region Free/Code Free Toshiba DVD player.
Great acting, writing and direction. The three legs of successful theater.
More like this show, please.
Will now move on to Water Rats; another Aussie drama, with a fine rep.
A great aussie drama but unfortuneately channel 7 decided to axe it the show during its second season
